CatDescriptText: David L. Lawrence was Mayor of the City of Pittsburgh 1946-1959, Governor of Pennsylvania 1959-1963, and he died in 1966.
TitMainTitle: Seven men, including Pittsburgh Mayor David L. Lawrence, and a woman, seated around table, with male portraits on wall in background, in the Office of the Mayor at the City County Building
